What is Auto Corretion of text?

Autocorrect is a type of software program that identifies miss-spelled words, uses algorithims to identify the words most likely to have been intended, and edits the text for you

Advantages of Auto-Correct:

-Improves productivity
-Intelligent corrections
-Saves time
-Gives you the right word and spells it correctly
-Discreet and easy to use

What is the use of AI?
 Computers have used machine learning algorithms in order to predict the word being typed based on the relevant context, and the data that the algorithm has collected and is processed locally on your device.
